    category: 'Contract Staffing',
    date: 'February 10, 2025',
    readTime: '7 min read',
    excerpt: 'Corp to Corp and W-2 are the two dominant contracting structures in US staffing — and choosing the wrong one exposes you to serious IRS and DOL risk. Here is how to decide.',
    coverEmoji: '🤝',
