        heading: 'The Right Model: AI Amplifies Human Judgment',
        body: `The most effective technical recruiting organisations in 2025 use AI to handle the tasks that do not require human judgment — parsing, initial scoring, scheduling, communications — and reserve human effort for the work that does: understanding team dynamics, assessing motivation, navigating negotiations, and building long-term candidate relationships.\n\nAt TalentNest HR, our AI layer handles the volume work. Our technical recruiters handle the judgment work. The result is the speed of AI with the quality that only experienced humans produce.`,
