    category: 'HR Technology',
    date: 'January 20, 2025',
    readTime: '8 min read',
    excerpt: 'If your team is managing hiring in spreadsheets and email threads, you are losing candidates, wasting recruiter hours, and making decisions without data. Here is what an HRMS actually does and when you need one.',
